summary: A thank you note.
body:
A thank you note.

I was considering what I’d want to Taylor if I’d ever get to meet her. I don’t want to write it all down here- because I feel like it’s something so personal there wouldn’t be any other way to say it than right there in front of her.

Obviously I’d want nothing more than to meet her and thank her in person, but I know my chances. I guess I’ve made peace with the fact that that’s not likely.

So although this may not be all I’d want to thank her for, it’s some of the things I’m eternally grateful for.

I want to thank Taylor for being the first person other than my own blood that I felt I could trust. I want to thank her for giving me a place where I felt I fit in when it seemed there was non. I want to thank her for showing me how to dream, for allowing me to fall in love with romantic fantasies. I want to thank her for her writing, as ultimately she’s the first reason for me to have wanted to do the same. I want to thank her for the lessons she’s taught me.

I want to thank her for not just being my friend, but everyone’s. All of us on this hellsite and others. Fan accounts, stan accounts, small ones, big ones- the amount of things she does for us and to be close to us is astounding to me. I want to thank her for standing with the world in the same places I do, like my place within the LGBTQ+ community.

Ultimately, I’m just grateful for her being who she is in this world and in my life.

So yeah, thank you @taylorswift

summary: Um. So. People have pointed out that a) this looks like part of a music video and b) that Taylor's nails in this picture remind...
body:
Um. So. People have pointed out that a) this looks like part of a music video and b) that Taylor’s nails in this picture remind them of her nails in the vertical Delicate music video - and ALSO it has been pointed out that her nails looked just the same the day of the iheartradio awards.

On THE SAME DAY (of the iheartradio awards) she posted three pictures:

The first two before the iheartradio awards

On the first ones her nails are painted just like they were later for the awardshow (and on the picture she posted yesterday). Now we can’t see her nails on the second picture but she’s wearing the same clothes, sunglasses and her hair looks the same so we can presume that both of these pictures were taken the day of the ihr awards.

On the second picture we can also see a big palm tree, which might be the middle tree of the legendary seven-palm-trees post - the one palm tree we all thought might stand for TS7.

Now the third picture is Taylor in her ihr awards outfit.

And remember how we all freaked out about her talking about the “butterfly migration in southern california” and then her wearing those butterfly heels?

I’d say that the butterflies are the connection between the first two pictures and the third - bc she clearlt wants her shoes to be seen as she lifts her leg.

ALSO remember how sge said we’d be the first to know about new music that same night? Yeah… Suspicious!

Now I don’t know what this all means BUT IT MEANS SOMETHING.

I think maybe she was filming a music video just before the ihr awards - maybe a song titled butterflies or wings or halo or angels (cause the wings would be a connection between butterflies and angels so maybe her talking about butterflies was a hint about a single called ‘angels’?).

ANYWAYS probably I’m just losing my mind but hey, who knows, @taylorswift has been planning and scheming for a long time for this one and at this point anything could happen…
